t the deployment of Odoc 3 to ocaml.org</li>

<li><a href=3D"https://jon.recoil.org/blog/2025/04/odoc-3.html">"Odoc 3: So=
 what?"</a> - in-depth explanation of Odoc 3's manual-focused features</li>

<li>Continued work on OCaml.org documentation pipeline integration through =
new package archiving tools</li>
</ul>

