<h2 id=3D"4">Chat plugin activated, and adding more site categories</h2>
<div class=3D"outline-text-2" id=3D"text-4">
<p>
Archive: <a href=3D"https://discuss.ocaml.org/t/chat-plugin-activated-and-a=
dding-more-site-categories/17220/1">https://discuss.ocaml.org/t/chat-plugin=
-activated-and-adding-more-site-categories/17220/1</a>
</p>
